    "data": [
        {
            "title": "黃仁勳與李在鎔等韓企會長吃炸雞 韓國相關股票成當紅炸子雞",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 黃仁勳吃炸雞在網路上爆紅，帶動韓國相關股票大漲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這位輝達執行長與三星電子執行會長李在鎔和現代汽車會長鄭義宣周四晚上在當地一家名為Kkanbu Chicken的餐廳吃炸雞、喝啤酒。Kkanbu並未上市，但三巨頭聚餐的照片和影片在社群媒體上爆紅後，該餐廳的競爭對手Kyochon F&amp;B Co.周五股價一度飆升了20%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">韓國家禽加工商Cherrybro Co.股價飆升30%漲停，交易量約為平均水平的200倍。在韓國創業板上市、生產炸雞機器人的Neuromeka Co.股價也大漲。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-99156491-467d-34e2-851d-e5c1462453cd-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一事件反映了韓國股市持續受到病毒式傳播和網路迷因的影響；尋求風險的交易員經常追逐與文化、政治或經濟熱點相關的短期收益。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Nvidia CEO Huang’s Outing Heats Up Korea’s Fried Chicken Stocks</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Elaine To.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%BB%83%E4%BB%81%E5%8B%B3%E8%88%87%E6%9D%8E%E5%9C%A8%E9%8E%94%E7%AD%89%E9%9F%93%E4%BC%81%E6%9C%83%E9%95%B7%E5%90%83%E7%82%B8%E9%9B%9E-%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%A8%E6%88%90%E7%95%B6%E7%B4%85%E7%82%B8%E5%AD%90%E9%9B%9E-032228853.html",
