            "title": "習近平在APEC呼籲維護供應鏈穩定暢通 中美先前達成貿易休戰協議",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 在會晤美國總統唐納德·川普並使全球最大規模的貿易戰得以休戰一年後，中國國家主席<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:習近平;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/習近平\">習近平</a>在首次的公開演講中堅持不要「斷鏈」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">習近平周五在韓國慶州舉行的亞太經合組織(APEC)領導人非正式會議上發表演說時表示，貿易夥伴應「積極尋找更多利益契合點，支持供應鏈開放發展」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這位中國領導人表示，堅持「拉手」而不是「鬆手」、「延鏈」而不是「斷鏈」，同時呼籲與會各方踐行「真正的多邊主義」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國財政部長斯科特·貝森特(川普貿易戰的主談人)也和其他受到美國全面關稅影響的世界領導人一同出席這項活動。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e5d8599e-cb79-3b8f-a3b0-380127de2e51-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">習近平發表上述演說的前一天與川普達成協議，美國暫停實施部分關稅和出口管制，中方恢復購買美國大豆並暫停實施對稀土的新出口管制。川普稱在釜山舉行的會談非常棒，習近平則強調對話比對抗好。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Xi Calls for Stable Supply Chains After Sealing Truce With Trump</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%9C%A8apec%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E7%B6%AD%E8%AD%B7%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E9%8F%88%E7%A9%A9%E5%AE%9A%E6%9A%A2%E9%80%9A-%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%88%E5%89%8D%E9%81%94%E6%88%90%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E4%BC%91%E6%88%B0%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-030230305.html",
